; Coverage test for xact.cc lines 932,934
; Tests the post_pred function with O_NOT and O_EQ operators in auto
; transactions. The quick matcher handles NOT and EQ predicates.

= not /Cash/
    (Budget:Spending)           -1.0

2024/01/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food              $50.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal
             $-50.00  Assets:Cash
             $-50.00  Budget:Spending
              $50.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
             $-50.00
end test
